## Interface: 11200
## Title: Teron's Modern Talents
## Author: Terongorus
## Notes: A custom talent tree window with glowing prereq connections, tier-lock indicators, and a Plan Mode for theorycrafting builds - inspired by the retail talent UI. Works on Turtle WoW and pure Vanilla 1.12.1.
## Version: 1.0.0
## DefaultState: enabled

## Dependencies: TeronModernCore

## SavedVariablesPerCharacter: ModernTalents_DB

# Talents
Talents\MSB_TalentCompat.lua
Talents\MSB_TalentPlans.lua
Talents\MSB_TalentIcon.lua
Talents\MSB_TalentConnection.lua
Talents\MSB_TalentGrid.lua
Talents\MSB_TalentExpanded.lua
Talents\MSB_TalentSettings.lua
Talents\MSB_TalentTree.lua
